	Example

	list = [1, 2, 3]
	new_list = list ++ [4]


	ğŸ“Œ list is unchanged.

	Interview line:

	â€œIn Elixir, data is immutable, so every transformation returns a new value, which avoids race conditions.â€

5.  Elixir collections (basic)

